Ashouf feek youm Ally enta 3malto feya ,lma enta ghadart beya welly bterdah Alaya bokra ana hardah Alik , Ashouf feek youm we Alaek taaban be garhak we btebky Ashan asamhak tebkily we ana afdal ad7ak w afrah mn Albi feek, kalamak tani mosh hayfedak mhaddesh drabak Ala eidak ashan tensa hob zaman , hatemshy bs mosh alaan hategy wabaa feek shamtan hatetab we lessa kamaan , ashouf feek youm yally seghert fe einaya law youm arabt leya lma tesallim alaya yomha ana haksef eidik klamak tani mosh hayfedak mhaddesh drabak ala eidak ashan tensa hob zaman hatemshy bs mosh alaan hategy wabaa feek shamtan hatetaab we lessa kmaaan